adsb-history-logger (0.3.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Track color now reads tar1090's own live ColorByAlt config at
    runtime instead of a hardcoded copy of stock SkyAware's values,
    which didn't match this install's actual (customized) config.js.
  * Fix History panel getting permanently stuck on "history
    unavailable" after one transient fetch failure (e.g. right after
    page load, before tar1090 has fully settled) -- it now retries
    automatically every 2s while the same aircraft stays selected.

 -- enbay1 <enbay1@gmail.com>  Tue, 21 Jul 2026 15:35:00 +0000

adsb-history-logger (0.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix history tracks not rendering at all (regression in 0.3.0). The
    direction-arrow code used ol.geom.Polygon, which tar1090's custom/
    trimmed OpenLayers bundle apparently doesn't expose (unlike
    LineString/Point, confirmed used directly by tar1090's own code) --
    the resulting exception was thrown before OLMap.addLayer() ran,
    silently dropping the already-built line segments too. Arrows now
    use LineString-only chevrons, and arrow failures are caught locally
    so they can no longer take the line rendering down with them.
    Errors are also now logged to the console instead of swallowed.

 -- enbay1 <enbay1@gmail.com>  Tue, 21 Jul 2026 15:10:00 +0000

adsb-history-logger (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * History tracks are now directional (arrow markers along the path,
    spaced evenly per visit) and colored by altitude using the same
    hue breakpoints as stock SkyAware's ColorByAlt (2000/10000/40000 ft
    -> hue 20/140/300, ground and unknown-altitude segments styled to
    match too), instead of a flat color.
  * track_geojson()/the /track/<icao> API now emit one small LineString
    segment per consecutive position pair (with altitude/on_ground/seq
    properties) instead of a single coordinates-only LineString, so a
    renderer can style each piece individually.

 -- enbay1 <enbay1@gmail.com>  Tue, 21 Jul 2026 14:30:00 +0000

adsb-history-logger (0.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix history-overlay.js using a relative API path ("history-api/"),
    which resolved incorrectly when tar1090 is mounted at a subpath
    (e.g. /tar1090/) -- requests silently hit lighttpd's 404 fallback
    (a 200 response of unrelated HTML) instead of the API, breaking
    the History panel for every aircraft. Now uses an absolute,
    root-anchored path ("/history-api/").

 -- enbay1 <enbay1@gmail.com>  Tue, 21 Jul 2026 13:15:00 +0000

adsb-history-logger (0.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix packaging: activate the debhelper python3 sequence so dh_python3
    actually runs. Without it, files installed to a build-machine-specific
    /usr/lib/python3.X/dist-packages path instead of the version-independent
    /usr/lib/python3/dist-packages, breaking the package on any target
    running a different Python 3 minor version than the CI runner.

 -- enbay1 <enbay1@gmail.com>  Tue, 21 Jul 2026 12:55:00 +0000

